octeon_instr_queue_t Struct Reference

#include <octeon_iq.h>

Detailed Description

The instruction (input) queue.

The input queue is used to post raw (instruction) mode data or packet data to Octeon device from the host. Each input queue (upto 4) for a Octeon device has one such structure to represent it.
